{"tid":1033273,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[怪癖] 我好中意跟住靚女後面 觀看人世百態","createTime":"2019-02-23T04:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-23T05:00:44.000Z","uid":234833,"like":17,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8490ce6e198e5c4fae8b6a5a1809c6c2565ebee8","tid":1033273,"uid":234833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T04:08:38.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次見到打對波出黎嘅女 抑或係氣質女<br />\n都好鍾意跟住佢地 <br />\n唔係話咩變態佬跟人地返屋企<br />\n而係好中意望迎面而黎嘅人嘅表情眼神<br />\n<br />\n男人通常會好快望一眼個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後勁快望落對波到<br />\n麻甩佬就會望住唔回避<br />\n甚至係過左之後擰轉頭再望下條短裙<br />\n西裝友就會扮晒野 用眼尾望下又避下咁<br />\n塊面扮係望向前 但對眼就跟住條女移動<br />\n以為唔顯眼其實就勁明顯<br />\n<br />\n女人都會望<br />\n會望樣 之後全身掃視 可能睇下衣著<br />\n最後會返返去個樣到<br />\n如果係雞格<br />\n女人眼神會帶點不屑 對眼有機會反一反<br />\n<br />\n憑住迎面而黎嘅人嘅眼神停留時間<br />\n眼神掃視及停留位置<br />\n宜家已經可以從後面估到前面個女仔究竟賣咩料<br />\n<br />\n自己好鍾意留意呢啲<br />\n有無同好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb15cf4928a38d79129cc28998c6c975984472b","tid":1033273,"uid":12259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T04:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b77a0da6e72c196c196312c62722f7abdcc6b43","tid":1033273,"uid":234833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T04:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa211157d8e06c70a1fddd743a9003c125dbd32a","tid":1033273,"uid":5196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T04:13:50.000Z","msg":"背多fun<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d2efb50845bc0d500afa2ff2803dfd73bfac4ac","tid":1033273,"uid":84998,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-0